  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-c63cbe24-0931-46b0-88e8-52fdf53d420a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70c042d3-7770-4b17-baa2-849a1c5ccb8f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d8376fad-d9fa-4bb7-acf7-8acd88450bac\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>백색인쇄 상식</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f704df47-7ae0-4dc8-a115-bdf3433dad70\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-438ec2ec-38bc-402e-a375-ff83057f9a31\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31688b62-ff9d-48eb-9982-0f88c8c8a2af\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄에서의 백색은 원래 종이색상을 말합니다. 특수잉크로 백색을 표현하지 않는다면 기본적으로 인쇄에서의 백색은 투명을 의미하며 인쇄인크가 묻지않는 부분의 종이의 색상이 그대로 표현되는 것을 의미합니다. 이 말은 그래픽 프로그램상으로 CMYK 0 으로 처리하면 이 부분은 어떤 개체도 종이의 색상이 표시된다는 의미입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4843e7f1-421e-4369-9cfc-737b1b749e65\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4a16a061-2d77-4901-a369-f6f46a4b6c7d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b8ada52-489b-4f03-97a5-8ce6951119d3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aecc4ac0-00e1-45c1-b08e-7466c251760d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">삼화제지에서 출시되는 밍크 쏠블랙, 랑데뷰 클래스 종이에 CMYK0로 인쇄한다면 종이색이 표현될겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-654d42ac-3be1-4d2e-b5c1-ee4cda46d70b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-532e5742-f615-4002-9ff4-efe0fec0e9aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de6f85d2-8aa3-4f5a-ba20-93055851be66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-93e0e343-62c0-4509-a442-f47f200de175\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://www.samwhapaper.com/product/samwhapaper/premium/41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.samwhapaper.com/product/samwhapaper/premium/41</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>  <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-329af969-4c65-4e78-a5e6-c15bfdb65ad6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6f1bb4da-6954-4156-8283-d09283099559\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fea8ab73-8c9e-4436-ae78-8135e031816e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe26b605-45fd-40da-aac4-a41776e1e522\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d004712b-fc4b-4b29-ac16-16baf3af012c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-f05758af-674c-4219-b03f-b9ab648f430a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ac597107-a620-4b5a-a534-b6dd7e0e8b21\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce3526e5-cdcc-420c-97b4-a44b813d9b7f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ed42b34a-5443-46d6-bb32-17f5210a0171\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이가 검은색, 비치색일 때 디자인이 표현되는 방법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f3bf132-903b-4101-ba67-1bb65415ba83\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eba071c4-58a1-45f1-8a90-43dbfdeb18e4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-33b211c0-1f9a-4812-a112-a882ece498a6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-33b211c0-1f9a-4812-a112-a882ece498a6\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTVfODcg/MDAxNjY1ODEzOTU3MzQ2.XFYtp3sDTEJPenbQXPtqG6GalvvsVl9TMyBXYPesQRQg.BBUmBULhbaYXjXW2tXJdLeItZryieuezQO9p8FPTyh4g.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2599\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1418\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTVfODcg/MDAxNjY1ODEzOTU3MzQ2.XFYtp3sDTEJPenbQXPtqG6GalvvsVl9TMyBXYPesQRQg.BBUmBULhbaYXjXW2tXJdLeItZryieuezQO9p8FPTyh4g.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b074278c-c4fc-4a32-a17d-4697b585cd83\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e195ec06-f93d-416b-8e41-20e926a9025f\" style=\"\">종이색에 따른 표현</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87e4755e-b28b-4f68-9258-e98e33f5d97c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b2187321-650e-49fb-8f69-7d27ffba35de\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-53970600-369c-4faa-8ddb-d6b8b3059d6d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aea02629-cf75-4850-95a8-6863c7789db2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-aea02629-cf75-4850-95a8-6863c7789db2\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTZfMTEy/MDAxNjY1ODQ2MzYwNjU5.pvD6W1GihvCUqdem7OUvsUfPhkMSMDbqzKcDFNdZBAkg.Km_akPKnu1ARMT2hwg5DGNAQBbn6tf4AYrCPiFcQQscg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2599\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1536\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTZfMTEy/MDAxNjY1ODQ2MzYwNjU5.pvD6W1GihvCUqdem7OUvsUfPhkMSMDbqzKcDFNdZBAkg.Km_akPKnu1ARMT2hwg5DGNAQBbn6tf4AYrCPiFcQQscg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-57774fc5-825a-435e-ade0-433a3087ddc1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1efab958-ef85-4850-a20d-a34d780ca28a\" style=\"\">검정종이에 컬러 표현</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-945cd0b8-2281-4f77-9084-243c43ccbdac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a9a9ed79-fe7f-430e-a331-4f39e68f7910\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7686ea00-219d-4b47-a5b4-515a08e0ef22\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a582248c-3d03-4499-9748-cc5a796409fa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dbb02299-dec8-46fe-8287-20bbdb2669c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이색에 따라 표현이 달라집니다. 그래서 종이는 거의 백색이나 미색이 70%이상입니다. 그 일반적인 종이에는 색상을 표현하는데 불편함이 없습니다. 그러나 종이가 특별한 색상이거나 검은색일때는 하얀색을 백색잉크를 사용하여 인쇄해야 표현이 됩니다. 그러면 왜 검은색으로 바탕을 표시하면 되는데 굳이 검은색 종이를 사용하는걸까요? 그 이유를 알아 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fcab5f9c-ad2b-4814-a977-50f437cdd0db\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6be803b0-07c0-44bf-8636-adf5c9607647\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6cb34aaf-49d0-4f8c-9ce1-482581950a88\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f62425e-53f9-4f87-aa59-8158aa767449\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오버프린트, 녹아웃에 대한 사항은 다음을 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b564ba21-e897-4358-9dbe-8b8cf720a879\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-187ca45e-56d4-4c4e-aa08-1c07aff2eaac\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222895566635\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222895566635</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>  <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e1507dfd-5c22-49c2-8512-4618fb3f6a75\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8efc734f-0058-4709-bad1-a6bf5ff3f1e7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38d508f3-81db-43e9-af75-c37ed65e473e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2f5ea3d5-8927-4ac0-bfa0-97ed2c0b3c46\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f953203-8dc1-4017-ac71-615d918e38db\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-a0c9831a-f475-4c51-bbb7-2574d4f49c04\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aad29bd3-6eae-419e-8aef-320d99f7d582\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1677d1dc-df5d-4122-ba93-0a742572d7da\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-faf2deae-958c-4348-a4c7-45a9bf001660\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>인쇄사고</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01d63c94-9f50-47ef-ac1f-2b0b2a85d74d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f16793c7-a3e3-496c-b183-9b533cb4df05\" style=\"color:#555555;\">굳이 종이의 색상을 복잡하게 바꾸는 이유는 뭘까요? 하얀 종이에 검은칠을 하면 똑같은 효과(?)를 볼 수 있는데 특별하게 종이를 바꾸는 이유는 여라가지가 있지만 크게 두가지만 말씀드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-78f5dcce-3097-4fd5-bea5-34e331c11cd1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-750bc934-fb39-4389-a600-ba8fc40ad5e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b0d6ebf-a546-4d03-b95f-61ecb4e3bdce\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2ef9cf6d-68ec-4e9e-8049-2ec8b618b3b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 뒷묻음</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d241072b-6a89-46c5-8f83-427445643824\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9114f7f7-194e-4641-9a57-ae2ffab50e98\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 후 잉크가 마르기 전에 재단을 하면 뒷묻음이 발생할 수 있습니다. 특히 검정색처럼 진한 색상뒤에 충분히 말리거나 UV인쇄를 하지 않는 경우 항상 뒷묻음의 사고는 발생할 수 있습니다. 특히나 합판인쇄의 경우 여러명함을 동시에 처리하는 프로세스라서 뒷묻음에 취약할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c766ffa0-3b37-48cf-98b6-2488a72c4557\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c766ffa0-3b37-48cf-98b6-2488a72c4557\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTVfMjU0/MDAxNjY1ODE1Njc4MDgz.A0IQq98-IZbRCdxa0R7zGtOtUeSk9DuGXISb_xJy_c4g.jfVjb00xm3a7OLmrI1ECHEiJiml5FYgnVHj7J_eVX_Ig.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1772\", \"originalHeight\" : \"709\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTVfMjU0/MDAxNjY1ODE1Njc4MDgz.A0IQq98-IZbRCdxa0R7zGtOtUeSk9DuGXISb_xJy_c4g.jfVjb00xm3a7OLmrI1ECHEiJiml5FYgnVHj7J_eVX_Ig.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eb13ecc5-d9f2-414f-9afe-6f8839397f43\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc8d1bff-d9a0-42eb-a6b9-6f8699ecdba7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cf0e420f-636a-4340-90af-78c09929fd17\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4525437-072c-4f3a-ac52-df1dc38d6892\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-87af29c4-c3c9-4e52-adf2-341ac44d54a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 색상의 층짐</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-15db086c-9c88-4f16-aeca-aadd1ae78254\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db91ca3c-e8cb-420a-b3aa-4f9298607b3f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄를 잘 진행하고 최고의 인쇄기기를 사용하더라도 첫장과 마지막장의 인쇄색상이 달라질 수 있습니다. 층짐현상은 일반적으로 발생할 수 있으며 또한 요즘처럼 여분지(야리지)를 아끼는 추세에서는 더욱 더 층짐이 발생될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8b13a7b2-0b05-41ce-aeb1-a4334d18119f\">\n<div class=